A mere 90 minute drive from Dubai and Sharjah international airports; only 20 minutes from bustling cities of Fujairah, Ras Al Khaimah; and few minutes away from vibrant downtown attractions. With 177 spacious guestrooms and lavish suites, exceptional dining establishments, outstanding recreational and leisure facilities including a championship golf course nearby, one of a kind dive sites and more, this luxury resort exemplifies a true escape. We are looking for:-Purchasing CoordinatorAvailability : immediate•	Obtain competitive quotations for hotel requirements and ensure that the best product is sourced and purchased, using group nominated suppliers where applicable•	Ensure locally nominated supplier information is kept current•	Manage the database of active local contracts with suppliers•	Adhere to quality procedures and standards and oversee purchasing administration •	Maintain a record of commitments for all budgets and ensure that the relevant senior managers are constantly informed of updates•	Ensure a comprehensive system for allocating and reconciling purchase orders•	Monitor all areas of purchasing including contracts, leases and nominations•	Prepare the month end accounts reports in an accurate and timely manner•	Execute on tasks/requests as instructed by the hotel managementAttractive salary with employment visa provided to all selected candidates.Please apply with your latest CV and photo now !!!
